comments: As Theis (BOS) retreats in a legal defensive position, Rubio (PHX) releases a pass that makes contact with Theis' (BOS) foot.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the foul committed by Booker (PHX) met the criteria for a clear path foul.
Waters (BOS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Booker (PHX) and firms up on his right leg.
Saric (PHX) briefly grasps Theis' (BOS) arm as he post up however, Theis (BOS) is able to defend through the marginal contact.
Ayton (PHX) receives the ball and immediately moves into his upward shooting motion.
Theis (BOS) makes contact to Ayton's (PHX) body after the release that does not affect his play at the basket.
Replay review of the foul called on Rubio (PHX) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Theis (BOS) maintains a legal position as he moves along Booker's (PHX) path following the pick.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Booker (PHX) and firms up on his left leg.
Hayward (BOS) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Smart (BOS) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Hayward (BOS) and Booker (PHX) mutually engage as they move to retrieve the loose ball.
Theis (BOS) commits a take foul on Ayton (PHX).
Waters (BOS) briefly grasps Rubio's (PHX) arm during the inbound.
Smart (BOS) makes contact with Booker (PHX) that affects his ability to get to the pass.
